(106, 83, '基礎材料', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:12.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">基礎材料種類及功能說明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.3pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">溫室整體結構於各種載重下<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>最終需經過基礎的整合設計以進行載重的傳遞於地面<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>並也承受拉拔的載重。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.3pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">溫室基礎受力模式則包含<span lang=\"EN-US\">Fx</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Fy</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Fz</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\"> Mxy</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Myz </span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mzx </span>等六個方向的作用力與力矩。而透過柱與柱底板、基礎螺絲與基礎形成力的傳遞奧平衡。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">基礎結構區分為強固型溫室基礎與簡易型溫室基礎。分別說明如下<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>主要基礎形式包含<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:62.1pt;mso-para-margin-left:3.18gd;\r\ntext-indent:-23.95pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">強固型基礎<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:12.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:62.1pt;mso-para-margin-left:3.18gd;\r\ntext-indent:-23.95pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">簡易型基礎<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'MIRDC UC', '2020-10-28 07:05:40', '2020-10-27 23:05:40'),
(107, 106, '強固型基礎', '<p>強固型基礎介紹</p>\r\n\r\n<p>強固型基礎分為獨立基礎、連續性條狀基礎。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>連續性條狀基礎已如地櫟的設計,相對結構安全穩固。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>獨立基礎施工較方便成本較低,主要區分為預製型基礎及現場澆鑄型基礎。基礎的作用在於基礎底板上的載重物質及基礎側邊的摩擦力的組合。但須考量其力的傳遞與拉拔抵抗。基礎的混凝土短柱頂高程應高於室 內地平線以免立柱柱腳受潮腐蝕,可高300〜500mm根據不同溫室的用途和現場情況而定。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>基礎結構材料以鋼筋混泥土建構,其鋼筋材料與混泥土材料及製造組合方法需注意材質、配給、施工、養生方式,以建立正確的基礎。基礎的鋼筋混泥土各自扮演載重及保護的功能。鋼筋與基礎螺絲的組合結構,其與溫室柱結構的連結具有高強度抗拉性能,以將溫室的各種載重傳遞到大地,其所受的載重除了六種基礎受力模式外,亦要對抗偶發性的地震力抵抗、長期受風動的疲勞反覆載重及地層的各種腐蝕環境負荷。</p>', 'MIRDC UC', '2020-11-25 03:37:25', '2020-11-24 19:37:25'),
(108, 107, '鋼筋', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(1)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">鋼筋使用普通鋼筋或竹節鋼筋。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(2)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">材質需由來源鋼廠出示材質證明及無輻射鋼筋證明。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(3)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">鋼筋形狀、尺寸、重量、精度需依設計管制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(4)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">鋼筋機械性能強度包含降伏強度、抗拉強度、延伸率。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'MIRDC UC', '2020-10-28 08:08:40', '2020-10-28 08:08:40'),
(109, 107, '基礎螺絲', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(1)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">基礎螺絲形狀、尺寸、精度均需依設計管制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(2)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">材質需有原廠材質證明。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(3)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">基礎螺絲性能強度包含降伏強度、抗拉強度、延伸率。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(4)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">基礎螺絲將扮演與地上溫室結構及地面基礎的連結<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>需注意其施工前及安裝後的防蝕處理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'MIRDC UC', '2020-10-28 08:09:00', '2020-10-28 08:09:00'),
(110, 107, '混凝土', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(1)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用符合<span lang=\"EN-US\">CNS61R2001(</span>波特蘭水泥<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>所規定之普通水泥<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>已凝結水泥不可使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(2)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">骨材粒料須清淨、堅硬、耐久<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>不可含有害的雜質、土、有機不純物等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(3)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">細、粗骨材隔開儲存<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>並注意土、垃圾等有害雑質的滲混。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(4)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">混凝土的級配<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>以能得到所要之強度、工作性、均勻性及持久而決定。級配的表示法及選擇<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>請參照中國土木工程師學會「鋼筋混凝土建築施工規範 」。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(5)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">混凝土拌合用水須清潔<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>無油、無酸、無齡、無鹽等<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>更不得使用海水。各種拌合料於每次拌合時正確計量<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;text-indent:-21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.77;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(6)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用預拌混凝土需依<span lang=\"EN-US\">CNSA2042</span>的規定。注意混凝土強度、塌度及混凝土量<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>到貨日時以一次到貨量控制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'MIRDC UC', '2020-10-28 08:09:32', '2020-10-28 08:09:32');
