(138, 137, '靜載重', '<p>1. 設施重量<br />\r\n設施重量依結構構架及外部被覆材詳實計算，並應考量固定於構架之裝備重量，例如固定於結構上之搬運設備、農用設備、照明設備、水槽、澆灌設備等等，須按實計算重量或依表1〜9之建議計算之。<br />\r\n表1 常用建築材料單位重</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">材料名稱</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">重量</span>(kg/m<sup>3</sup>)</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">材料名稱</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">重量</span>(kg/m<sup>3</sup>)</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:138px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">普通黏土</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none